{"tid":783345,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"777fb直播　稱不同意單程證內地人搶走港人資源","createTime":"2018-08-17T12:46:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-17T14:35:06.000Z","uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":50,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"4364c59e2548b1ac47905cd0ecab2c224fcd9317","tid":783345,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T12:46:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1413071-20180817.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1413071-20180817.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=gymw88FKLZleXhCH8leI0uPnIAwyWqphGIcg0J4V%2Buw%3D&h=c37e816a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1413071-20180817.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=ae4ed17a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1413071-20180817.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n行政長官林鄭月娥在facebook個人專頁直播，就將於10月發表的施政報告，諮詢網民意見。林鄭月娥在開場時解釋，本屆政府重視創意和互動，因此接受年輕同事的意見，在社交網站與網民互動。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥回應網民提出，取消每日150個單程證配額。她說，這是回歸前制訂的入境政策，讓港人在內地的配偶和子女，來港家庭團聚。她認為這是人權，反問網民為何不歡迎有關政策。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥說，不同意使用單程證來港的內地人士，搶走港人資源的說法。她認為本港出生率低、人口老化問題嚴重，有生力軍來港，反而帶來更多新血，協助推動經濟發展。"},{"pid":"fed59ecb436bbfe7675c09c55cee54d1885316ba","tid":783345,"uid":70786,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T12:47:22.000Z","msg":"150人唔係問題來源係Easy target <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但又講唔出理據<br />\n淨係叫你地要接受佢地<br />\n話有d仲係激進份子會去佔中扮撚晒親切<br />\n咁林鄭你放激進份子落嚟香港係咪反中亂港呢?"},{"pid":"ae112ccb6a8ca23f8af59e413d09560e5485d907","tid":783345,"uid":137506,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T12:47:37.000Z","msg":"收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 再收落去香港就嚟陸沉"},{"pid":"d35d8dc5f10cd8112ebd1e33c6a996af7500ebd9","tid":783345,"uid":198583,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T12:48:52.000Z","msg":"Main